import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'

import {Router, Route, hashHistory } from 'react-router'

ReactDOM.render(
  <Router history={hashHistory}>
    <Route path='/' component={App}/>
  </Router>
    ,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
